# welcome to the passageJS project!

**<<typewriter speed="20">>this is a project intended to be an alternative to Twine or even RenPY. with custom animations, smart transitions, and infinite scalability<</typewriter>>**

<<typewriter speed="50">>so I have but one simple question.
what are you here for?<</typewriter>>

[[to become a contributor|contributor/landing]]  
[[to use this in my story|usage/landing]]  
